This package is the repo-owned hook point for installing DAPHNE firmware
overlay assets into a PetaLinux image.

Planned payload once the build handoff is wired:
- daphne3_st_OL_<gitsha>.dtbo
- daphne3_st_OL_<gitsha>.bin
- shell.json

Source of truth:
- xilinx/output/
- scripts/package/complete_dtbo_bundle.sh
